### Core Methods

- `Board.__init__`: Initializes the board with the appropriate pieces.
- `Piece.__init__`: Initializes a piece with its color.
- `Player.__init__`: Initializes a player with their set of pieces.
- `Game.__init__`: Initializes a new game.
- `Game.initialize_board`: Sets up the initial positions of the pieces on the board.
- `Game.print_board`: Prints the current state of the board to the console.
- `Game.get_valid_moves`: Returns all valid moves for a given player.
- `Game.make_move`: Updates the board state based on a move.
- `Game.check_winner`: Determines if there is a winner.

